#. <section class="sutta" id="sn5.3"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn5.3:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 5"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 5"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn5.3:0.2"
msgid "1. Bhikkhunīvagga"
msgstr "1. Nuns"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 3. Kisāgotamīsutta → gotamīsuttaṃ (bj, s1-3) | gotamī (pts1)
msgctxt "sn5.3:0.3"
msgid "3. Kisāgotamīsutta"
msgstr "3. With Kisāgotamī"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts1ed" id="pts1ed1.130"></a>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.285"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn5.3:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn5.3:1.2"
msgid ""
"Atha kho kisāgotamī bhikkhunī pubbaṇhasamayaṃ nivāsetvā pattacīvaramādāya "
"sāvatthiṃ piṇḍāya pāvisi."
msgstr ""
"Then the nun Kisāgotamī robed up in the morning and, taking her bowl and "
"robe, entered Sāvatthī for alms."

msgctxt "sn5.3:1.3"
msgid ""
"Sāvatthiyaṃ piṇḍāya caritvā pacchābhattaṃ piṇḍapātapaṭikkantā yena "
"andhavanaṃ tenupasaṅkami, upasaṅkamitvā divāvihārāya."
msgstr ""
"She wandered for alms in Sāvatthī. After the meal, on her return from alms-"
"round, she went to the Blind Man’s Wood,"

msgctxt "sn5.3:1.4"
msgid "Andhavanaṃ ajjhogāhetvā aññatarasmiṃ rukkhamūle divāvihāraṃ nisīdi."
msgstr ""
"plunged deep into it, and sat at the root of a tree for the day’s meditation."

msgctxt "sn5.3:1.5"
msgid ""
"Atha kho māro pāpimā kisāgotamiyā bhikkhuniyā bhayaṃ chambhitattaṃ "
"lomahaṃsaṃ uppādetukāmo samādhimhā cāvetukāmo yena kisāgotamī bhikkhunī "
"tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā kisāgotamiṃ bhikkhuniṃ gāthāya ajjhabhāsi:"
msgstr ""
"Then Māra the Wicked, wanting to make the nun Kisāgotamī feel fear, terror, "
"and goosebumps, wanting to make her fall away from immersion, went up to her "
"and addressed her in verse:"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn5.3:2.1"
msgid "“Kiṃ nu tvaṃ mataputtāva,"
msgstr "“Why do you sit alone and cry"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn5.3:2.2"
msgid "ekamāsi rudammukhī;"
msgstr "as if your children have died?"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn5.3:2.3"
msgid "Vanamajjhagatā ekā,"
msgstr "You’ve come to the woods all alone—"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn5.3:2.4"
msgid "purisaṃ nu gavesasī”ti."
msgstr "you must be looking for a man!”"

#. </p></blockquote><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn5.3:3.1"
msgid "Atha kho kisāgotamiyā bhikkhuniyā etadahosi:"
msgstr "Then the nun Kisāgotamī thought:"

msgctxt "sn5.3:3.2"
msgid "“ko nu khvāyaṃ manusso vā amanusso vā gāthaṃ bhāsatī”ti?"
msgstr "“Who’s speaking this verse, a human or a non-human?”"

msgctxt "sn5.3:3.3"
msgid "Atha kho kisāgotamiyā bhikkhuniyā etadahosi:"
msgstr "Then she thought:"

msgctxt "sn5.3:3.4"
msgid ""
"“māro kho ayaṃ pāpimā mama bhayaṃ chambhitattaṃ lomahaṃsaṃ uppādetukāmo "
"samādhimhā cāvetukāmo gāthaṃ bhāsatī”ti."
msgstr ""
"“This is Māra the Wicked, wanting to make me feel fear, terror, and "
"goosebumps, wanting to make me fall away from immersion!”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn5.3:4.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho kisāgotamī bhikkhunī “māro ayaṃ pāpimā” iti viditvā māraṃ "
"pāpimantaṃ gāthāhi paccabhāsi:"
msgstr ""
"Then Kisāgotamī, knowing that this was Māra the Wicked, replied to him in "
"verse:"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn5.3:5.1"
msgid "“Accantaṃ mataputtāmhi,"
msgstr "“I’ve got over the death of children,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn5.3:5.2"
msgid "purisā etadantikā;"
msgstr "and I’m finished with men."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn5.3:5.3"
msgid "Na socāmi na rodāmi,"
msgstr "I don’t grieve or lament,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn5.3:5.4"
msgid "na taṃ bhāyāmi āvuso."
msgstr "and I’m not afraid of you, sir!"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.286"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "sn5.3:6.1"
msgid "Sabbattha vihatā nandī,"
msgstr "Relishing is destroyed in every respect,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn5.3:6.2"
msgid "tamokkhandho padālito;"
msgstr "and the mass of darkness is shattered."

#. <br>
#. VAR: Jetvāna maccuno → jetvā namucino (si)
msgctxt "sn5.3:6.3"
msgid "Jetvāna maccuno senaṃ,"
msgstr "I’ve defeated the army of death,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn5.3:6.4"
msgid "viharāmi anāsavā”ti."
msgstr "and live without defilements.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "sn5.3:7.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho māro pāpimā “jānāti maṃ kisāgotamī bhikkhunī”ti dukkhī dummano "
"tatthevantaradhāyīti."
msgstr ""
"Then Māra the Wicked, thinking, “The nun Kisāgotamī knows me!” miserable and "
"sad, vanished right there."
